oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Blacksmith shop
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of a blacksmith shop in Noah with ads on the exterior of the building. Men, children and horses are posed in front of the shop. The two men standing in the shop are holding hammers over an anvil.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
